The Red Sea Restaurant & Bar
Liked by
faint4lent

  • beab.mpls

    Pivot presents Ratio at the Red Sea this December 6th

    For this Ratio, we are bringing back the back-to-back night so be ready for a heavy knocking night brought to you by 6 DJs (3 B2Bs)

    Entering the Ratio ring for the first time around are Heavyweight champions Asher Gray (@asherdgray) and Greyhound (@greyhoundgreyhound)
    Hailing from Milwaukee, these two have been prominent figures in Wisconsins own dance scene by hosting many events throughout the state, opening for Fred Again and as well as individually having put out releases. Recently, Asher Gray has put together a label called Club Ritual (@clubritual) and the first release is under Greyhound, so be sure to give that a check

    Ratio alumni Real Girl (@realgirlthedj) and Ori the Ghost (@oritheghost) will be playing together under a new alias titled SUBPLEASER that will absolutely devastate (or please) any SUB within a mile radius, so proceed with caution while the girls play

    Setting the stage for the night, Beab (@beab.mpls) will be playing alongside Enigma mastermind Akko (@akkobeats). Akko had played at the last B2B Ratio extravaganza and crushed it, so it makes sense to invite him back into the ring.

    Lastly, we are excited to be working with Greyphoria Sound (@greyphoriasound)this time around for all of our sound system needs. If you have ever been to any Unbothered party, youll know that this system indeeds slaps.

    Hope to see you in the ring

    We will have early bird $10 tickets up on RA, so grab them while you can!

    Links in bio!

    Info:
    21+
    Date - 12/06/24
    Location - Red Sea (320 Cedar Ave South, Minneapolis, MN 55454)
    Time - 9PM to 2AM
    Cover - $15 (Cash, Venmo, RA)
    Sound - Greyphoria Sound

    Lineup and Times
    Akko + Beab - 9:00PM to 10:40PM
    Greyhound + Asher Gray - 10:40PM to 12:20AM
    SUBPLEASER - 12:20AM to 2:00AM

    *Note: Please reach out if the cover price is something you cant afford but want to still go to the event
